5ambRqdTJt9vGwFzVI9HBw
I hadn't been here in years and it's changed so much! And for the better. The coffee is reasonably priced, which means it's cheaper than Starbucks (and has higher quality beans), and the vibe is really laid back. If you're sick of going into super snobby coffee shops - go here!   I ordered an iced latte with almond milk. Unfortunately, the almond milk started to separate. It's fine to drink, but pretty unappealing. I asked if they would remake it with soy milk and they did it without question. There is plenty of seating indoor and outdoor and I will definitely be back the next time I'm in town. I can see why this place is my friend's favorite!

