I've been to the other Green location in Tempe many times (which is always great) - and I tried this one for the first time yesterday. Seems like it's in a great location and it definitely stands out. The service was friendly and quick and the food was fresh, hot, and delicious. I would recommend their veggie burgers to anyone - they are made there and are unlike any I have had. Love this place!

